<section class="case" id="case">
  <div class="case-headings">
    <h2 class="case-case">CASE</h2>
    <h2 class="case-study">STUDY</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="case-content">
    <p class="case-paragraph">
      I am currently working as a freelance software engineer specializing in Umbraco systems. Over the years, I've contributed to large-scale web applications for clients like Jesperhus, Maus and Inet. I have extensive experience collaborating with international companies, with a strong focus on the Scandinavian market.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .case {
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: clip;
  }

  .case-headings {
    position: absolute;
    top: 15%;
    left: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .case-case {
    animation: case-move 6s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .case-study {
    animation: study-move 8s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .case-content {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-bottom: 50px;
    max-width: 40%;
    align-self: end;
  }

  .case-paragraph {
    color: var(--nord5);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  @keyframes case-move {
    0% { transform: translateX(0); }
    100% { transform: translateX(50px); }
  }

  @keyframes study-move {
    0% { transform: translateX(50vw); }
    100% { transform: translateX(4ch); }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .case-case,
    .case-study {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
